# vibe-shop API örnekleri — VS Code REST Client / IntelliJ HTTP Client ile çalıştırılabilir.
# Önkoşul: `make start` (veya `docker compose up -d` + migration + `go run ./cmd/server`).
# Kimlik: Keycloak (http://localhost:8081, realm vibe-shop). Kullanıcılar Keycloak'ta yönetilir;
# API'nin kendi register/login ucu yoktur. Test kullanıcıları realm import'uyla hazır gelir.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@keycloakUrl = http://localhost:8081

### Sağlık kontrolü → 200 {"status":"ok"}
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Ürünleri listele (public) → 200, JSON dizi
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products

### Tek ürün getir (public) → 200
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### Olmayan ürün → 404 {"error":"product not found"}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/9999

### Geçersiz id → 400 {"error":"invalid product id"}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/not-a-number

### Keycloak'tan token al (testuser) → 200 {"access_token":"..."}
# @name kcLogin
POST {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/vibe-shop/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=vibe-shop-api&username=testuser&password=test1234

### Keycloak'tan token al (testuser2 — izolasyon denemeleri için) → 200
# @name kcLogin2
POST {{keycloakUrl}}/realms/vibe-shop/protocol/openid-connect/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

grant_type=password&client_id=vibe-shop-api&username=testuser2&password=test1234

### Ürün ekle (Keycloak token'ı gerekir) → 201, oluşturulan ürün (id dahil)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"name": "Tabak", "price": 49.90}

### Ürün ekle — token'sız → 401 {"error":"missing or malformed authorization header"}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Korsan Tabak", "price": 9.90}

### Ürün ekle — gövdedeki id yok sayılır → 201, sunucu id üretir
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"id": 424242, "name": "Vazo", "price": 10}

### Ürün ekle — boş name → 400 {"error":"name must not be empty"}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"name": "", "price": 10}

### Ürün ekle — price <= 0 → 400 {"error":"price must be greater than zero"}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"name": "Fincan", "price": 0}

### Ürün güncelle (tam güncelleme, token gerekir) → 200, son hali
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"name": "Tabak", "price": 59.90}

### Ürün güncelle — token'sız → 401
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/4
Content-Type: application/json

{"name": "Tabak", "price": 1.00}

### Olmayan ürünü güncelle → 404 {"error":"product not found"}
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/products/9999
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"name": "Hayalet", "price": 10}

### Ürün sil (token gerekir) → 204, boş gövde
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/3
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Ürün sil — token'sız → 401
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/products/3

### Sepete ekle → 201, kalem (aynı ürünü tekrar eklemek quantity artırır)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

{"product_id": 1, "quantity": 2}

### Sepeti görüntüle → 200 {"items":[...],"total":...}
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### İzolasyon: testuser2'nin sepeti ayrıdır → 200, boş liste
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin2.response.body.access_token}}

### Token'sız sepet → 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/cart

### Sipariş ver → 201, sipariş (items + total, fiyatlar o anki değeriyle sabitlenir; sepet boşalır)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Boş sepetle sipariş → 400 {"error":"cart is empty"}
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{kcLogin.response.body.access_token}}

### Token'sız sipariş → 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders

### Kaldırılan uçlar: register/login artık Keycloak'ta → 404
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{"email": "ali@example.com", "password": "artik-yok"}
